data.description: Dream Home! Turn key, newly updated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home. Located on desirable Villa Dr. where you won't miss out on events such as Trunk or Treat or Christmas Villas. Upon entering you will see a spacious open concept layout and top of the line CALI Bamboo flooring. The remodeled kitchen counters and soft close cabinets add a modern home feel. The multiple vinyl windows allow for an abundance ofnatural lighting throughout the home. Step out to the backyard to relish in the thriving fresh herbsand vegetable garden. The chicken coop around the corner is ready for your very own home raised  chickens. Make this spectacular home yours! All offers welcome!
